 border-left: 1px solid rgb(12, 137, 24); border-top-color: rgb(12, 137, 24); border-right-color: rgb(12, 137, 24); border-bottom-color: rgb(12, 137, 24);\"><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">民间传说孕妇不能吃螃蟹，据说是因为螃蟹属“大凉”之物，孕妇吃多了容易流产；此外，从食物性味上讲，性寒的除了螃蟹，还有西瓜、冬瓜、苦瓜、大白菜……这类食物都被指“太寒”孕妇不能吃。在广为流传的孕期饮食讲究中，孕妇吃兔肉也是大忌。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">这些传言是真的吗？</span></p></section></section></section></section><p style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" label=\"Copyright © 2015 Yead All Rights Reserved.\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin: 5px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center;\"><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"34405\" data-color=\"rgb(172, 29, 16)\" data-custom=\"rgb(172, 29, 16)\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em auto 0.3em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 1em; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(254, 254, 254); border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); display: inline-block; width: 590px;\"><section class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.2em; font-size: 1em; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(172, 29, 16);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify;\">流产和食物关联不大，染色体异常是主因</span>&nbsp;</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 0px; border-top: 0.6em solid rgb(172, 29, 16); border-bottom-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); height: 10px; border-left: 1em solid transparent !important; border-right: 1em solid transparent !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></section></section></section></section></section></section><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; text-align: justify; font-family: 微软雅黑; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><font color=\"#3e3e3e\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">对于身体健康的孕妈咪而言</font><font color=\"#3e3e3e\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">滑胎食物的说法太夸张了，盲目信从只会导致孕妈咪在饮食上忌口很多，出现营养不良的情况。</font></span></p><p style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: justify; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">“关螃蟹西瓜什么事？自然流产，是因准妈妈肚子的胚胎不够‘壮’！&nbsp;&nbsp;多数自然流产发生在12孕周之内（即孕早期），而原因多半数是<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\">胚胎染色体异常</span></strong>所致；此外，孕妇的精神高度紧张焦虑、内分泌失调或生殖道异常、生殖道感染以及男方精子质量不好等也可能导致流产，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\">临床上还没听说过日常普通饮食为直接原因而导致自然流产的</span></strong>。</span></p><p style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><p style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 微软雅黑;\">怀孕确实是个特殊的生理时期，科学合理的饮食有利于胎儿的健康发育和成长。但事实上，很多孕妇对饮食太过关注，反而容易忽视其他影响因素。孕早期要顺利度过，除了饮食均衡、<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\">营养要跟得上</span></strong>外，更要<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">避免过大的工作压力</strong></span>，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(239, 112, 96);\">保持舒畅的心情，注意孕期卫生、防止生殖道感染</span></strong>等，以免增大自然流产的风险。</span></p><p style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"></p><section class=\"\" data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"34405\" data-color=\"rgb(172, 29, 16)\" data-custom=\"rgb(172, 29, 16)\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(62, 62, 62); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section class=\"\" style=\"margin: 0.8em auto 0.3em; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: initial; border-style: none; border-color: initial;\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 1em; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; text-decoration: inherit; color: rgb(254, 254, 254); border-color: rgb(172, 29, 16); display: inline-block; width: 590px;\"><section class=\"\" data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-heigh