INSERT INTO `forestry_type` VALUES ('56', '企业号微信认证申请流程', '<h1 style=\"margin: 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; line-height: 50px; font-size: 24px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif;\">企业号微信认证申请流程</h1><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif;\">企业号微信认证（即由注册号到认证号的流程），可以通过以下方法申请，开始认证后，请根据页面提示操作，目前只有企业号创建者才可发起认证。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif;\">申请入口：请在电脑端打开qy.weixin.qq.com，登录企业号管理端，设置-&gt;进入认证系统-&gt;输入帐户密码-&gt;开通。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://file.service.qq.com/user-files/uploads/201707/0e4368edb529c49b5a183a56f20e0abe.jpg\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); outline: none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://file.service.qq.com/user-files/uploads/201707/c787b575e4d723fcf78a5a83891396d1.jpg\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); outline: none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://file.service.qq.com/user-files/uploads/201707/b5ae4c71c5955eb678f976ff2ff957a2.jpg\" style=\"margin: 15px 0px 25px; padding: 0px; border: 1px solid rgb(229, 229, 229); outline: none; vertical-align: middle; max-width: 100%;\"></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: center;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif;\"><font color=\"#008000\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">温馨提示：</font></div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;, &quot;microsoft yahei&quot;, sans-serif;\">1、微信企业号申请微信认证，需一次性支付300元/次审核服务费用（政府除外）。认证无论成功或失败，我们都需要支付给第三方审核机构的成本费用（审核服务费）。</div><div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(102, 102, 102); font-family: &quot;helvetica neue&quot;, arial, &quot;hiragino sans gb&quot;,